<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idef780699-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s2225d"><num value="2225d">§ 2225d.</num><heading> Availability of Department of Agriculture funds for temporary employment</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">On and after <date date="2005-11-10">November 10, 2005</date>, funds appropriated by this or any other Appropriations Act to the Department of Agriculture (excluding the Forest Service) shall be available for employment pursuant to the second sentence of <ref href="/us/usc/t7/s2225">section 2225 of this title</ref> and <ref href="/us/usc/t5/s3109">section 3109 of title 5</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idef78069a-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/97/tVII/s703">Pub. L. 109–97, title VII, § 703</ref>, <date date="2005-11-10">Nov. 10, 2005</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/119/2149">119 Stat. 2149</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
